@* Features Section *@
<section id="features" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Özellikler</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">BIAnalytics ile verilerinizi görselleştirin, analiz edin ve raporlayın.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            @* Card 1: Gelişmiş Dashboard Export *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">file_download</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Gelişmiş Dashboard Export</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Dashboard içerisinde yer alan tüm raporlar tek bir Excel dosyası olarak indirilebilir. Chart'ları tek tek veya seçerek export alma esnekliği.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 2: Sürükle-Bırak Dashboard Tasarımı *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-indigo-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-indigo-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">dashboard_customize</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Sürükle-Bırak Dashboard Tasarımı</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Teknik bilgiye ihtiyaç duymadan görsel bileşen kütüphanesinden seçim yaparak saniyeler içinde kişisel raporlar ve dashboard'lar tasarlayın.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 3: Evrensel Veri Konnektörleri *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-purple-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/20 to-purple-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">hub</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Evrensel Veri Konnektörleri</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Excel, SAP, Google Analytics ve özel veritabanları dahil her türlü veri kaynağı ile entegre çalışır. Farklı sistemlerden veriler tek platformda.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 4: Alerts & Zamanlanmış Raporlama *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-amber-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-amber-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/20 to-amber-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">notifications_active</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Alerts & Zamanlanmış Raporlama</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Kurumsal raporlama ihtiyaçlarının temel bileşenlerinden biri olan zamanlanmış raporlar, PDF export ve otomatik e-posta gönderimi.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 5: Full Data CSV Export *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-emerald-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
