            </div>

            @* Card 9: Yüksek Performanslı Büyük Veri Desteği *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-violet-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-violet-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
