                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Büyük veri senaryolarında yüksek performans sunacak şekilde optimize edilmiş. Yoğun veri hacmiyle çalışan kurumsal raporlama için uygundur.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 10: Refresh & Scheduling *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-teal-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-teal-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/20 to-teal-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">autorenew</span>
