                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Dashboard'ların belirlenen periyotlarla otomatik yenilenmesi ve cache'e kaydedilmesi. Kullanıcılar her zaman güncel verilerle çalışır.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 11: Row Grouping & Grouped Headers *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-pink-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-pink-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-pink-500 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/20 to-pink-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">view_list</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Row Grouping & Grouped Headers</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Tablolarda tekrar eden satırlar gruplanarak sade görünüm. Excel export'a birebir yansır. Çok seviyeli gruplama desteği.</p>
            </div>

            @* Card 12: Column Totals & Reverse Table *@
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-lime-500/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-lime-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-lime-600 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-500/20 to-lime-500/5 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">calculate</span>
